data.description: This 2 Bedroom Row Home is completely remodeled from top to bottom.  New Roof; New Kitchen; New Bath; New Floors and Carpeting; New Windows; Fixtures; New Hot Water Heater.    As you enter from the Front Porch into the Living Room, you will find a freshly painted Home, Formal Dining Room, Kitchen with New Countertops, New  Stainless Steel Sink, Garbage Disposal, Built in Microwave and New Refrigerator.  New Bathroom. Deck off Kitchen and Off Street Parking. The Second Floor has 2 nice size Bedrooms.  Why pay rent when you could own a Home.  This affordable Home is worth seeing!!!
